{
  "script_id": "qr-decomposition",
  "voice": "zh-CN-YunxiNeural",
  "voice_key": "yunxi",
  "files": [
    {
      "script_id": "qr-decomposition",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-1",
      "filename": "intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/qr-decomposition/yunxi/intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.9,
      "size": 30384,
      "text": "一个矩阵的各列，往往彼此歪斜、纠缠不清。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "qr-decomposition",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/qr-decomposition/yunxi/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.65,
      "size": 26352,
      "text": "QR 分解要做的，是把它拆成两块干净的结构。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "qr-decomposition",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/qr-decomposition/yunxi/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.97,
      "size": 31536,
      "text": "一块是列彼此垂直的正交阵 Q，一块是上三角阵 R。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "qr-decomposition",
      "section_id": "gs",
      "line_id": "gs-1",
      "filename": "gs-gs-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/qr-decomposition/yunxi/gs-gs-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.58,
      "size": 25344,
      "text": "第一列直接单位化，作为第一个正交方向。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "qr-decomposition",
      "section_id": "gs",
      "line_id": "gs-2",
      "filename": "gs-gs-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/qr-decomposition/yunxi/gs-gs-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.27,
      "size": 36288,
      "text": "第二列减去它在第一个方向上的投影，剩下的部分就与前者垂直。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "qr-decomposition",
      "section_id": "gs",
      "line_id": "gs-3",
      "filename": "gs-gs-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/qr-decomposition/yunxi/gs-gs-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.34,
      "size": 37440,
      "text": "逐列这样投影相减、再单位化，就得到一组两两正交的单位向量。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "qr-decomposition",
      "section_id": "qr",
      "line_id": "qr-1",
      "filename": "qr-qr-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/qr-decomposition/yunxi/qr-qr-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.75,
      "size": 43920,
      "text": "这些正交单位向量并排，就是正交阵 Q，满足 Q 转置乘 Q 等于单位阵。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "qr-decomposition",
      "section_id": "qr",
      "line_id": "qr-2",
      "filename": "qr-qr-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/qr-decomposition/yunxi/qr-qr-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.29,
      "size": 36720,
      "text": "而正交化时减掉的每个投影系数，恰好被记录进上三角阵 R。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "qr-decomposition",
      "section_id": "qr",
      "line_id": "qr-3",
      "filename": "qr-qr-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/qr-decomposition/yunxi/qr-qr-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.78,
      "size": 28512,
      "text": "R 的对角线，就是每一列减去投影后剩下的长度。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "qr-decomposition",
      "section_id": "verify",
      "line_id": "ver-1",
      "filename": "verify-ver-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/qr-decomposition/yunxi/verify-ver-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.77,
      "size": 28368,
      "text": "把 Q 与 R 乘回去，正好还原出原始矩阵 A。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "qr-decomposition",
      "section_id": "verify",
      "line_id": "ver-2",
      "filename": "verify-ver-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/qr-decomposition/yunxi/verify-ver-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.92,
      "size": 30672,
      "text": "因为 R 记下了如何用正交基重新组合出每一列。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "qr-decomposition",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-1",
      "filename": "interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/qr-decomposition/yunxi/interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.3,
      "size": 36864,
      "text": "切换不同矩阵，看虚线的原始列如何被拉成实线的正交列。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "qr-decomposition",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-2",
      "filename": "interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/qr-decomposition/yunxi/interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.08,
      "size": 33264,
      "text": "对照右侧的 Q 与 R 表格，验证它们相乘就是原矩阵。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "qr-decomposition",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-1",
      "filename": "summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/qr-decomposition/yunxi/summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.98,
      "size": 31680,
      "text": "QR 分解把矩阵拆成正交阵 Q 与上三角阵 R。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "qr-decomposition",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-2",
      "filename": "summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/qr-decomposition/yunxi/summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.46,
      "size": 39312,
      "text": "它由 Gram-Schmidt 正交化得来，是最小二乘和 QR 特征值算法的基石。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "qr-decomposition",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-3",
      "filename": "summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/qr-decomposition/yunxi/summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.81,
      "size": 28944,
      "text": "把歪斜化作正交，让计算变得清爽，我们下次再见！"
    }
  ],
  "total_duration": 32.85,
